title: Trying on the Rubber Suit | American Horror Stories - "Rubber (Wo)man - Part One" (HD Clip)
author: AHS Crave
comment: The most supernatural thing in this scene is how she managed to put the suit on by herself with no talc or lube in just a few minutes and get it perfectly stretched over her body.
I like to tape a rubber ball in my mouth when I go for a jog, it’s kind of a running gag.
She fit the suit absolutely perfectly
So now I can wear a gimp suit to con and if they ask I'll just say I'm cosplaying as the rubberwoman from AHS
When someone discovers a new kink they like and get scared by it. xD
